queries.sql: SELECT `tb1`.*, `tb2`.`title` as `name_faculty`, `tb3`.`title` as `name_class`, `tb4`.`title` as `name_cat`, `tb5`.`name` as `name_city`, `tb6`.`name` as `name_district`, `tb7`.`name` as `name_ward`, `tb8`.`name` as `name_ethnic`, `tb9`.`name` as `name_religion` FROM `users` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `faculties` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`faculty_id` = `tb2`.`id` INNER JOIN `classes` as `tb3` ON `tb1`.`class_id` = `tb3`.`id` INNER JOIN `user_catalogues` as `tb4` ON `tb1`.`user_catalogue_id` = `tb4`.`id` LEFT JOIN `vn_province` as `tb5` ON `tb1`.`countryside_cityid` = `tb5`.`provinceid` LEFT JOIN `vn_district` as `tb6` ON `tb1`.`countryside_districtid` = `tb6`.`districtid` LEFT JOIN `vn_ward` as `tb7` ON `tb1`.`countryside_wardid` = `tb7`.`wardid` LEFT JOIN `vn_ethnic` as `tb8` ON `tb1`.`ethnic` = `tb8`.`id` LEFT JOIN `vn_religion` as `tb9` ON `tb1`.`religion` = `tb9`.`id` WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`faculty_id` = '1' ORDER BY `id` asc LIMIT 20

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`email`, `tb1`.`phone`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb1`.`fullname`, `tb1`.`user_catalogue_id`, ( SELECT tb2.title FROM user_catalogues as tb2 WHERE tb1.user_catalogue_id = tb2.id) as `job` FROM `users` as `tb1` WHERE `email` = 'phamdoanh24@gmail.com'

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`email`, `tb1`.`phone`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb1`.`fullname`, `tb1`.`user_catalogue_id`, ( SELECT tb2.title FROM user_catalogues as tb2 WHERE tb1.user_catalogue_id = tb2.id) as `job` FROM `users` as `tb1` WHERE `email` = 'phamdoanh24@gmail.com'
